network.link

Class Link

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.link.Link

  • public class Link
extends java.lang.Object
    Link is the class representing a directed link between a transcription factor or regulatory gene and a target node. A LinkProperties is attached which can hold additional information about the link.
    Since:
    0.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Joeri Ruyssinck (joeri.ruysssinck@intec.ugent.be)
